translated: East Timor, East Timor or Timor-Leste (short forms) or the Democratic Republic of East Timor (long form) is a listed country, according to geographers, Asia (traditional position) 12 or Oceania.
original: Le Timor oriental, Timor-Oriental ou Timor-Leste (formes courtes), ou la République démocratique de Timor oriental (forme longue), est un pays classé, selon les géographes, en Asie (position traditionnelle)12 ou en Océanie.
